 </sub>
 <italic class="italic">… R</italic>
 <sub class="sub">3,10</sub>]
 <sup class="sup">T</sup>, 
 <italic class="italic">m</italic> is the soil C pool, ranging from 1–3, 
 <italic class="italic">n</italic> is the soil layer ranging from 1–10.
