 <italic class="italic">j</italic> is a donating pool, and the blank in the matrix 
 <bold class="bold">F</bold> are zeros. 
 <italic class="italic">ξ</italic> is environmental modifier, a product of temperature scalar, water scalar, depth scalar, and oxygen scalar as in Koven et al.
 <sup class="sup">
  <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR11" class="xref">11</xref>
